Z","msg":"我都好希望，求巴打推一推。"},{"pid":"83554a6bacea4264a07031c8308cb9d527985efc","tid":1531261,"uid":229385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"宜家係咩事？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋成個9月冇行動呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n係咪要完啦我想問？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打咗90日，我哋終於將香港議題打到上國際層面<br />\n終於呼喚到外國勢力<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">或者會</span></span></strong>幫我哋立一條保障我哋嘅法案<br />\n正當美國準備復會，我哋竟然收聲？<br />\n你叫美國點通過呀？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會<br />\n全連登唔該力推9月8日再集結<br />\n一氣呵成，通過香港民主及人權法案！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsCuBrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsCuBrf.jpg&h=ba764316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">機會只得一次！！<br />\n2019年錯過，將永遠唔會返嚟</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6ddadde3431b4a9e24a914395cab8b8ff71578c4","tid":1531261,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37ee825e7de82f80f20c852d97607f819e7536a9","tid":1531261,"uid":298893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80a5b7f871bb8a26e522eee103a156a87a0d7eb4","tid":1531261,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未爛未拆 咁樣入！</strong></span></span><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/